\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{1}{p_{n}}$
\end_inset

收敛当且仅当级数
\begin_inset Formula $\sum_{n=1}^{\infty}\frac{n}{p_{1}+\cdots+p_{n}}$
\end_inset

收敛.
\end_layout

